<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.2">
<l>kontār tuḷava malarkoṇ ṭaṇivāṉē</l>
<l>nantā taperum pukaḻvē tiyarnāṅkūr</l>
<l>centā marainīrt tiruveḷ ḷakkuḷattuḷ</l>
<l>entā yaṭiyē ṉiṭaraik kaḷaiyāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One who is adorned with flower-clustered tulasī blossoms,</l>
<l>My father in Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam with red lotuses in the water</l>
<l>In Nāṅkūr with Vedic experts of flawless great fame,</l>
<l>Cast off the suffering of your servant, me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
